text: Laura Michelle Kelly (born 4 March 1981) is an English actress and singer. She played Mary Poppins in the musical of the same name. She also played Sylvia Llewelyn Davies in Finding Neverland on Broadway. Kelly made her movie debut in 2007 as Lucy Barker in the Tim Burton 2007 movie Sweeney Todd: The Demon Barber of Fleet Street. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English voice actors Category:English stage actors Category:Actors from Hampshire Category:English singers Category:English dancers
